org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Dependability.StateBased.StateBasedComponents

Interface StatefulHardware

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DependableComponent, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StatefulHardwareImpl

    public interface StatefulHardware
extends DependableComponent
    A representation of the model object 'Stateful Hardware'. obsolete, see SimpleStochasticBehaviour

    The following features are supported:

    • Prob Perm Fault
    • Error Latency
    • Repair Delay
    • Fault Occ
    See Also:
    StateBasedComponentsPackage.getStatefulHardware()
